380
00:28:34,380 --> 00:28:36,640
Dal Bongu?

381
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:40,050
Proč to musí být takhle?

382
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:42,630
Nedává to vůbec smysl.

383
00:28:56,610 --> 00:28:59,263
- Kang Jaeji.
